pr_body:
The following pull request focuses to increase the test coverage of the currently implemented test suite for Neutralinojs CLI.

- [x]  Write tests for `neu plugins` command.
- [x]  Write tests for `neu version` command.
- [x]   Write tests for `neu update` command.
- [x]   Write tests for `neu build` command.
